                    </div>
                    <span>This book's strength is that it is basically an outline of good strategy development. Another reviewer called it the book for "dummies"-like that was a criticism. It provides an excellent guide for real managers trying to get a tough job done in competition with their "real job" requirements. If you need something to impress a teacher, buy something different. If you need to get some strategic planning done in the typical workplace, put this book high on your list of resources.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Should be titled "Simple Strategic Planning"</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
